# Input

```yml
&flowseq [
 a: b,
 &c c: d,
 { &e e: f },
 &g { g: h }
]

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1 +1,6 @@
-&flowseq [a: b, &c c: d, { &e e: f }, &g { g: h }]
+&flowseq [
+ a: b,
+ &c c: d,
+ { &e e: f },
+ &g { g: h }
+]
\ No newline at end of file
```

